{"tid":1122429,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北辰促撤回修訂","createTime":"2019-04-24T03:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T04:07:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37316fa4a6d6f2de7476e3dbb715ecf31b694ece","tid":1122429,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190424/20662750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190424%2F20662750&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubMQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=45fe7d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190424%2F20662750&h=891a308f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190424/20662750</a><br />\n<br />\n田北辰促撤回修訂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190424/large/24la5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190424%2Flarge%2F24la5p4.jpg&h=b0dc9631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田北辰<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府一直以陳同佳涉台灣殺人案為由推動修訂，但陳涉及的洗黑錢案最快或在本月底獲釋，意味政府或未能趕及修例，身兼港區人大代表、實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰接受《明報》訪問時指，立會月底甚至7月休會前通過修例機會渺茫，力促政府先撤回現有修訂，否則若表決法案時涉案人已離港，自己不會投票，建議政府應先針對台灣殺人案修例。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：泛民街站痛陳禍害打工仔反送中：驚老闆撤離<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌反對直上大會<br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂草案委員會首次會議未能選出正、副主席後，工聯會郭偉強揚言考慮引用《議事規則》第91條將修訂直接提交大會審議。<br />\n<br />\n至今未就修例表明投票立場的自由黨黨魁鍾國斌昨稱不贊同郭的提議，指審議法案是立法會的角色，並指議員在法案委員會可以提出修正案完善修例，亦會召開公聽會，若取消實屬不妥，「如果直上大會，疑問冇人解答，冇修正，係好壞嘅情況」。鍾國斌重申，議員需要監察政府，「唔應該為個別情況放棄自己權力，否則係不負責任」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n泛民街站痛陳禍害 打工仔反送中：驚老闆撤離<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營︰民主黨倒娥 北京中間人索料 (季陶)<br />\n<br />\n泛民街站痛陳禍害打工仔反送中：驚老闆撤離"},{"pid":"567632760488e55b20dcbf421fd0dd35193074fa","tid":1122429,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"直立廿三條？"},{"pid":"321316ece9b6d8d4fa0126c60ed5468fadbffaf9","tid":1122429,"uid":156321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"驚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3d1fb5fec0612ed9a0f9d9d4e5dc007f4914f6","tid":1122429,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"遮名以為泛民議員講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842604f8bdc6c5e613077caa14fd4738b5b63a5e","tid":1122429,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c3d1fb5fec0612ed9a0f9d9d4e5dc007f4914f6","tid":1122429,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"遮名以為泛民議員講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"關鍵一席"}]}